title: HOUR 2- Kyle Long Sep 14, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 2- Kyle Long Sep 14, 2020
description:
Kyle Long tells Dan what it is like to be a football commentator rather than being on the field playing for the Bears. Kyle admits to Dan that he may not be done playing and says he may re-evaluate his playing career after this season.
